{"tid":237593,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"燒味美食店清單","createTime":"2017-05-10T12:58:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-15T11:36:51.000Z","uid":62277,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"279dff40cc9730b9e40722c2436dbc92bb49799f","tid":237593,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T12:58:51.000Z","msg":"純粹個人口味<br />\n排名順序<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1)元朗 添記<br />\n推介: 燒肉<br />\n<br />\n皮脆,食落有炭燒香味<br />\n肉質鬆軟,肥瘦相間<br />\n唔會乾<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/clsuaoxr\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fclsuaoxr&h=07624f12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/gev96hty\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fgev96hty&h=968d0836&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n燒雞都唔錯<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/qgywh38a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fqgywh38a&h=2a98696b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2)旺角 齒留香<br />\n推介: 叉燒<br />\n<br />\n色水靚,有光澤<br />\n有燶邊,燒得香<br />\n肉質腍嫩,蜜味啱啱好<br />\n惟一缺點係腌味偏重<br />\n唔係好食得出肉既鮮味<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/zrfg08n6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fzrfg08n6&h=5c88426b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3)樂富 食棧<br />\n推介:燒鵝<br />\n<br />\n鵝油甘香<br />\n又唔會好似一樂油得太過份<br />\n食落有種似係荔枝既芳香<br />\n皮都尚算脆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ur8pd91m\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fur8pd91m&h=b917dac3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n叉燒唔好食<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/bj86z1pa\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fbj86z1pa&h=11a6aa42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/490hf63q\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F490hf63q&h=dacb7086&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4)上環 龍邦<br />\n推介: 叉燒<br />\n<br />\n水準正常嗰日真係無乜邊間夠佢黎<br />\n比齒留香蜜味更實在<br />\n而且食到肉既鮮味<br />\n質感係我鍾意有咬口、鬆化嗰隻<br />\n唔係得個腍字<br />\n不過佢水準唔太穩定<br />\n好似星期一至六午飯時段會好食d<br />\n暫時未完全掌握清楚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/syidkew8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fsyidkew8&h=92fe6b8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/rugem6j5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Frugem6j5&h=cef44b40&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"604c0621abd3fdda14333d920cee937660e58278","tid":237593,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T13:03:37.000Z","msg":"最驚D叉燒太甜<br />\n試過一間甜過蜜祖"},{"pid":"cb91029c36ef10cd1e4cdd2bb8d3c18c69231e10","tid":237593,"uid":82254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T13:10:50.000Z","msg":"入嚟就係想講龍邦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申上環撚"},{"pid":"3a27ca3898faec3e099a0dcf800547cb0ff5f39c","tid":237593,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T13:54:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>入嚟就係想講龍邦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申上環撚</blockquote><br />\n龍邦+1<br />\n少啲吹奏佢啦，一陣多人食又跌watt"},{"pid":"5f4b77d845df87ac0d8a3941fe3322453f6a8480","tid":237593,"uid":1096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T14:01:55.000Z","msg":"一樂叉燒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00fbcf448a7aba71a1b13e87748a1ab3fdbff64c","tid":237593,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T14:04:28.000Z","msg":"正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6c561aa5844734e8d68bdbe8511f4afc75671e0","tid":237593,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T14:07:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最驚D叉燒太甜<br />\n試過一間甜過蜜祖</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n太興嗰d都